SUMMARY:Deadline: Structurist Creative Research Fellowship (4th round)
DESCRIPTION:The University of Saskatchewan Art Galleries offer the Structur
 ist Creative Research Fellowship\, supporting art-and-science research-cre
 ation engaging The Structurist\, the art and architecture journal publishe
 d at the university from 1960 to 2010. The fellowship provides a project b
 udget of up to CAD 20\,000 plus travel and accommodation for the Saskatoon
  component. Open internationally at any career stage. Deadline 31 August 2
 026.\n\nOrganisation: University of Saskatchewan Art Galleries and Collect
 ion\nLocation: Saskatoon\, Canada (travel and accommodation covered for th
 e Saskatoon component). Open internationally\, any career stage.\nAward: P
 roject budget up to CAD 20\,000\, plus travel and accommodation for the Sa
 skatoon research component. No application fee.\nDuration: Research-creati
 on fellowship around The Structurist journal archive.\n\nMore: https://kag
 cag.usask.ca/engage/special-projects/structurist/fellowship.php?utm_source
 =artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
URL:https://kagcag.usask.ca/engage/special-projects/structurist/fellowship.
 php?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
LOCATION:Saskatoon\, Canada (travel and accommodation covered for the Saska
 toon component). Open internationally\, any career stage.
